thread.title: Angela Cornford-Scott

author: Angela Cornford-Scott
title: Angela Cornford-Scott
text: Servcorp was a great place to start my business. The way they structure their services gave me the flexibility to manage the way I used them, which for a new business is a great option to have. The staff were always very helpful and friendly. They are also very quick to pick up the little things which matter. I am very pleased to have had their support.
